text: This classic traditional home boasts a well-designed plan, defined living spaces, high-end finishes, and thoughtful details throughout. Step inside to find rich wood floors, neutral paint, decorative lighting, and an inviting atmosphere. Formal dining room is complimented by a butlers pantry, making it perfect for entertaining. Island kitchen features painted cabs, granite countertops, stainless appliances, and ample prep and storage space, making it a chefs delight. A built-in entertainment center adds charm and functionality to the living area. Upstairs, the primary suite is a retreat, with sitting area and a private balcony overlooking the backyard. The spa-like ensuite bath offers relaxation. Sink in utility room conveniently located on the second floor. A fourth bedroom with its own ensuite bath provides privacy for guests or family members. Enjoy expansive backyard oasis, complete with a sparkling pool and spa. Three-car garage offers parking and storage. As Southlake is renowned for incredible parks and recreation this home is perfectly positioned to take advantage of them. Minutes away, find sports fields, walking trails, playgrounds, state-of-the-art tennis center, Nature Center, and equestrian trails. Love the water? Grapevine Lake is a short drive offering access to boating, fishing, paddle boarding, and hiking trails. Historic Main Street in Grapevine offers boutique shopping, fine dining, wineries, and year-round festivals, including Grapevine Christmas Capital of Texas events. This home is just minutes from gourmet grocery shopping, top-rated schools, and easy access to DFW Airport and major business and financial centers.
